---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Contact | Belt Tuner">
  <h1>Contact</h1>
  
  <p>Have a question, feedback, or want to contribute a verified frequency for a new printer model?</p>

  <h2>GitHub</h2>
  <p>The best way to reach out or contribute is via our GitHub repository. You can open an issue or submit a pull request if you want to add a new printer to the database.</p>
  <p><a href="https://github.com/yourusername/belt-tuner" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Visit the GitHub Repository</a></p>

  <h2>Email</h2>
  <p>For direct inquiries, you can reach out via email at: <a href="mailto:support@belttuner.com">support@belttuner.com</a></p>

  <style>
    h1, h2 {
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-top: var(--space-6);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    }
    p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
